					<img src="https://i0.wp.com/metro.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/SEC_71516033.jpg?quality=90&#038;strip=all&#038;crop=0px%2C0px%2C841px%2C630px&#038;resize=480%2C360&#038;zoom=1&#038;ssl=1" class="attachment-hero_image wp-post-image nf-image" alt="&#8216;Purged&#8217; North Korean official turns up at event with Kim Jong Un">
					<span class="icon icon-"></span>
				</a>
			</div>
			<header class="nf-headline"><h3 class="nf-title"><a data-track="tag/news-feed/news-feed-title25" href="https://metro.co.uk/2019/06/03/purged-north-korean-official-turns-event-kim-jong-un-9778050/" title="&#8216;Purged&#8217; North Korean official turns up at event with Kim Jong Un" >&#8216;Purged&#8217; North Korean official turns up at event with Kim Jong Un</a></h3>
			</header>
			<div class="nf-content">
			<div class="nf-excerpt">There were reports he had been sentenced to hard labor and ideological re-education over the failed summit in Hanoi in February. </div>
			</div>
